* Industry standards were followed for the manufacture and quality control of these receivers;

* Ammonia is not corrosive in this service and the vessels are relatively new;

* Safety relief valves limit operating pressures in these receivers;

* The facility has a preventive maintenance program in place to maintain the ongoing integrity of the vessels;

* The facility has a training program designed to ensure that the system is operated by qualified personnel;

